HEADWORD: Quinicine
<hw>Quin"i*cine</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <fld>(Chem.)</fld>
<def>An uncrystallizable alkaloid obtained by the action of heat from
quinine, with which it is isomeric.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

